{"id": 1916, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些类型的“安可”上瘾症，你看了就想笑？", "description": "就是那种，离开是为了被挽留，的假动作。（题图来自：Pixabay)", "record_count": 9013, "comment_count": 41, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170919050730xUr8sbC4i3GLPjep.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-21T17:00:49Z", "questions": [{"id": 3003, "title": "哪些类型的“安可”上瘾症，你看了就想笑？", "content": "你都见过哪些类型的“安可”上瘾症？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 236488, "content": "多人团体各自单飞，但每隔几年总要合体纪念一下过去的流动型体质", "image": "img/option/option/20170919042930iRNgGnK8SBMxb6tJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236489, "content": "告别演唱会开了几百场，对歌坛还是放不下的十八相送型", "image": "img/option/option/20170919042957g1vsSRHz3u74anfY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236490, "content": "到年纪息影之后依然兢兢业业几年一部电影的发挥余热型", "image": "img/option/option/20170919043028i8XklmH9tEIQs075.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236491, "content": "关掉博客声称要休息，几个月后憋了个大招开始卖东西的转换跑道型", "image": "img/option/option/20170919043236W25s3NYknJx8wOVj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236492, "content": "关评论弃号后突然变豁达，回归时强调不在意别人的看法的遁入空门型 ", "image": "img/option/option/20170919043226TsCcYMW4IrJak1iS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236493, "content": "洗白过去，风波过去了又默默上线的风头避趋型", "image": "img/option/option/20170919043315rHFwlSmC0z3kPXsf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236494, "content": "近期没有作品，但在真人秀里强势回归型", "image": "img/option/option/201709190433389U7FbZG5NgE4fdOr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 236495, "content": "挡不住的文思泉涌，封笔之后再出山，续集喷涌型", "image": "img/option/option/20170919043405VUmLYJ54tzCZPDc2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}